{"tid":1750623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六點半到七點半投票率只輕微高於上屆同一時間0.13個百分點！！！","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T13:08:39.000Z","uid":339805,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"90a86cd316319195b1c162ffa5cb5fe957a4a330","tid":1750623,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"18:30至19:30間的投票率為3.29%，只輕微高於上屆同一時間0.13個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dStJFj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdStJFj1.png&h=09373395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n距離區議會選舉投票截止時間僅兩小時。眾新聞將過去12小時的累積投票率數字，轉化為每小時投票率作分析，可見今屆的投票高峰期是09:30至10:30，投票率為7.02%。隨後每小時投票率逐步減少，至18:30至19:30間的投票率為3.29%，只輕微高於上屆同一時間0.13個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1011700552506687/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1011700552506687%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=cd32ae06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1011700552506687/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e4f772eed07a4e57b253304e3836d4b3ed03d465","tid":1750623,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投資，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3b9e5d240bdbb82fbcec70a6f88c5b32e1a45ce6","tid":1750623,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"估計會一路跌落去"},{"pid":"63f6c92fbd813d3cbf041344a4437a243678f68a","tid":1750623,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b04e58081a9346f9c264e5198cff4117598f1f0","tid":1750623,"uid":208118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"高開低走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d9f7d0189af388398951460ced3aefa7c97cd3","tid":1750623,"uid":177644,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"其實好正常姐 投得既都投哂 逐步遞減好正常 唔明寫黎有咩價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8afd18c6f0b22c6f2d1a03bf4cd6c79b75fcac","tid":1750623,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b04e58081a9346f9c264e5198cff4117598f1f0","tid":1750623,"uid":208118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"高開低走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"300萬人唔失禮"},{"pid":"68d7d121ae053602776b32465871a8ba8f87309a","tid":1750623,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91d9f7d0189af388398951460ced3aefa7c97cd3","tid":1750623,"uid":177644,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"其實好正常姐 投得既都投哂 逐步遞減好正常 唔明寫黎有咩價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:59:46.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0280372b102b72a0c00317c049c3da3